{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"874faca7e6","title":"神·鬼·人","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6263f38892","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":26,"articleId":"874faca7e6"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00b690bae1","name":"清华大学"},{"id":"f0784f753b","name":"保中(孙宝琮)"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"20679f2484","type":"title","text":"神·鬼·人","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"},{"id":"15b5ab1498","type":"authors","text":"清华大学保中(孙宝琮)","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"},{"id":"83cb69391d","type":"subtitle","text":"(保中，即孙宝琮：清华大学电机系学生。1953年入校，后转入工程物理系。因在苏共20大之后政治表现“异常”，被转回电机系工业企业电气化专业91班。)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"},{"id":"4397280a79","type":"subtitle","text":"（《庶民报》社论：一切为了帮助党政风，一切为了社会主义）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"},{"id":"5aea79c5a9","type":"paragraph","text":"人敬神而畏鬼，但也有人是敬鬼神而远之，这样就连神带鬼一起都畏了。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"},{"id":"497a5be0e4","type":"paragraph","text":"人之所以敬神是因为神能给人带来吉祥，人之所以畏鬼是因为鬼能给人带来灾难。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"},{"id":"72946b06e4","type":"paragraph","text":"因而，畏鬼情有可原；但畏神却令人费解！说来这是人的悲剧。人无不想近神，而多得吉祥，而神无不想近人，以尽神责。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"},{"id":"de2356b167","type":"paragraph","text":"而何竟相畏？想系神居天阙，难以呼人吸，久而久之，竟渐染鬼习。竟认：“人神不同，人是被怜悯者，神是恩施者。人听命于天，而神主宰万物。凡夫俗子——人，特殊材料——神，”人脑迟心钝，难解神意，稍一不慎，何堪神击！这样，人就“敬鬼神而远之”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"},{"id":"19116875dd","type":"paragraph","text":"这就是人的悲剧！愿：人里不再出“神”，而“神”永在人间。则庶民万幸！祖国万幸！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"},{"id":"d942913ce1","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：黄延复《五七风暴》。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6"}],"page":{"id":"2cb7dbdb24","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"874faca7e6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}